reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are great for the price
reviews.reviewText: Pretty notebooks are getting very expensive. This 3 pack was a great deal. This is a very useful size and the outer covers are very thick and sturdy. The elastic band keeps used pages together when you don't want them removed. If you don't need all three, the extra ones would make a great addition to gift baskets or Christmas stockings. They also have a very large selection of designs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I LOVE THIS NOTEBOOK !
reviews.reviewText: I love this notebook.There is a beautiful black background with flowers, on the front cover and back cover. The cover is thick and sturdy and does not bend or rip. It is also amazing that the cover is waterproof ... I had my notebook next to my drink which accidentally spilled, and the notebook just wiped clean and remained dry and unchanged.I love the doubled spiral binding. There are always times when you need to remove a page ... either you made a mistake, or you need to pull a page loose from the book for some reason ... and if there is no spiral, and you tear out a page, then the whole book can fall apart. So, a spiral binding is important to me.The pages are thick, so that when you write with a marker, it does not bleed through to the other side. So, you can write on both sides of a page without it showing through.The pages are lined, for easy writing. At the top right side of each page, there is small print that says "Date" and "No." You can use this if you need it, or ignore it if you dont need it, because it is printed small and light.There are two added bonuses to this book ...(1) At the back, there is an envelope pouch glued to the inside of the back cover. I didn't think that it was important, until I needed it and used it. The pouch expands just a little bit, enough to hold a bulky item, but not enough to keep the notebook from closing properly. I put envelopes with important mail in there. And I put pages that I tore out but then needed to keep. And I put business cards. It is nice to put these loose items in the book and know that they will not fall out.(2) There is a gold elastic ribbon that wraps from the back of the book to the front. You can use this to keep the book firmly closed, so that if the book is in your purse, it cannot open. It also keeps loose papers safe and protected. And, you can use the ribbon as a book mark, so if you wrote on a page and dont want to have to flip through the whole book to find it, you can wrap the ribbon over that page.I appreciate this book because I use it constantly. On one page, I wrote a list of all of my medications ... doctors are always asking what pills I am taking, what doses, how often ... and I just open the book and show it. On another page, I wrote a list of questions for my doctor so that I dont forget to ask, and I listed all of my upcoming appointments. On another page, I wrote out a shopping list of items that I always need, so that when I go to the supermarket, I wont forget anything. On another page, I wrote a list of my bills and due dates and expenses, so that I can keep track of them. And, I love to write poems ... I copied over my favorite poems that I wrote, and I look at them when I am in a waiting room or standing on line, it is better than a magazine. And, of course, I use the book to write down little notes or reminders as they come up.I know that I will fill up this book very quickly. When all of the pages are used, I intend to keep it, and then buy another one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful but some printing issues
reviews.reviewText: These notebooks are exactly what I was looking for and they are beautiful. The covers are sturdy and vibrant. The paper is good weight, no bleed through at all and nicely lined. Except, one of the notebooks had some pages that were not lined like the other pages. So maybe check them out before gifting them to someone. They are very gift worthy other than that. I am just going to use the unlined pages to add ephemera! I still recommend these notebooks.

reviews.reviewText: These are gorgeous notebooks. Love the spiral binding. Vivid colors. Absolutely perfect for journaling, taking notes you want to keep. Love the band on the side to hold it together, protects the pages. In between college rule and wide rule. Perfect. 3 pack is great, great price. Will buy again.

De pasta dura, bien montados en espiral y con hojas de papel de muy buena calidad, es muy agradable escribir en ellos.

J'adores ces cahiers de notes. En plus, ils ne sont vraiment pas cher pour 3. Ils ont beaucoup de pages sans l'impression d'avoir un gros livres. Les pages sont super épaisses et rigides (l'encre de feutres passe tout de même à travers). Elles tournent très bien dans la spirale et ne semblent vraiment pas vouloir en sortir. Je les utilise depuis 6 mois et l'élastique est comme au premier jour. Il y a une pochette à la fin. Je ne pourrais pas la commenter, je ne l'utilise pas. La spirale est parfaite pour insérer un stylo et être toujours prête à écrire. Ils sont assez petit pour les transporter dans mon petit sac à dos et même dans un sac à main. La texture de la couverture est très agréable. Elle est très douce. Les couleurs sont un peu plus foncées que sur les images selon moi.
